  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to libdbusmenu-qt</title>

    <para>
      The <application>libdbusmenu-qt</application> package contains a library
      that provides a Qt5 implementation of the DBusMenu protocol.
    </para>

    &lfs76_checked;

